### Get Low Stock Items
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/inventory?lowStock=true&page=1&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Update Product Stock
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/inventory/{{productId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
